OMERO Common
    JAR file:  omero-common-3.0-Beta3.jar
    URL:       http://trac.openmicroscopy.org.uk/omero/wiki/MilestoneDownloads
    Notes:     used by OME I/O to connect to OMERO servers
    License:   GPL

OMERO Importer
    JAR file:  omero-importer-3.0-Beta3.jar
